{
  "chapter": 221,
  "chapter_summary": "朱姬在马车中向项少龙倾诉心事，流露出对项少龙又爱又恨的复杂感情，并识破黑龙为假。项少龙因部下国兴被管中邪射杀而悲愤难平，在宴会上当众向管中邪搦战。吕不韦试图阻止，嫪毐却趁机煽动，小盘与朱姬准予比武。两人第三次对决，管中邪采取轻灵战术避实就虚，但项少龙以命搏命、舍刀鞘单刀应敌，百战刀法已达宗师境界。管中邪渐落下风之际，吕娘蓉冒死扑出救下管中邪，项少龙虽重伤对手却未能取其性命，功亏一篑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！我往后该怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "对不起！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后何出此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我自己都不知自己在做什么，但有些时候，我真恨不得有人可把你杀了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我绝不会怪太后的，无论怎样，我都不会怪你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那条黑龙究竟是真是假，求你不要瞒我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "当然是真的，要假能假得来吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你生气了，有时我真希望你可以打我、骂我，那人家还会好受一点。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我太熟悉你了。只从你刚才答话的神态，就知道那是条假龙，这么厉害的计策，定是你想出来的，没有人比你更会装神弄鬼了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "此刻我真想狠狠揍姬后一顿！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "管中邪在哪里？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙想怎样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三绝才女果是名不虚传，一曲虽罢，但我耳内仍像缭绕着她动人的歌声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "我要杀死管中邪！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙三思！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "微臣上趟与管大人比武一事，因管大人剑断而止，今见管大人另佩宝刃，忽感手痒，望能与管大人再比试一场以作助兴，请储君与太后赐准。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚乃大喜之日，不宜妄动刀兵，少龙若因私人恩怨……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仲父此言差矣，上回难道是仲父大悲之日吗？为何仲父却一力主战？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项统领果然眼利，看出卑职新佩的齐国名剑射日非是凡品，不易折断，故动了雅兴，若储君、太后和仲父赐准，中邪乐于奉陪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这才是我大秦的好男儿，请太后赐准。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我大秦向以武力卫国，两位卿家正体现了我大秦的尚武精神，准予所请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停手！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "吕娘蓉",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "中邪！你怎样哩？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "中邪受教，此刀永不敢忘。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不赶快救人治伤！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 221,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    }
  ],
